name: Skelly's Late Laser Flip
description:
First Ever Monochrome Skelly!! Was so inspired by all the monochrome artist I found during the #hen500k event, I had to try one! Hats off to all the MC artists out there! This is by far the most labor intensive Skelly to date.

GIF image - 15.5 MB on disk - 960x723px RGB - 140 original hand drawn frames/slides/sketches Rotoscope style animation.
